text: Mohammed Abdel-Jawad (born May 1, 1979) is a Palestinian footballer who plays as a Central defender for Palestine football club Al-Birah. In 1994, he served as the team's captain. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Palestinian footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Palestine international footballers
